          "text": "6.5 濡備綍浣跨敤鎵嬪姩鐪熺┖",
          "text_id": "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.1.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "**鏂规硶涓€锛堝湪鑷姩鐪熺┖杩囩▼涓垏鎹㈣嚦 Pulse Vac 妯″紡锛夛細**",
          "text_id": "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.2.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "step_flow",
          "steps": [
            {
              "id": "step1",
              "text": "闀挎寜 [btn:Pulse Vac] 鎸夐敭杩涜鐪熺┖鎶芥皵銆?",
              "text_id": "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.3.step.step1.text"
            },
            {
              "id": "step2",
              "text": "鏉惧紑鎸夐敭鍒欐殏鍋滄娊姘斻€?",
              "text_id": "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.3.step.step2.text"
            },
            {
              "id": "step3",
              "text": "杈惧埌鎵€闇€鐪熺┖鐘舵€佸悗锛岀偣鍑?[btn:Seal] 鎸夐敭杩涜瀵嗗皝銆?",
              "text_id": "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.3.step.step3.text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "**鏂规硶浜岋紙鐩存帴浣跨敤 Pulse Vac 妯″紡锛夛細**",
          "text_id": "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.4.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "step_flow",
          "steps": [
            {
              "id": "step1",
              "text": "灏嗚鍙ｆ斁鍏ョ湡绌鸿厰銆?",
              "text_id": "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step1.text"
            },
            {
              "id": "step2",
              "text": "鍏抽棴闈㈢洊锛屽苟涓嬪帇鎶婃墜浠ラ攣绱ч潰鐩栥€?",
              "text_id": "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step2.text"
            },
            {
              "id": "step3",
              "text": "闀挎寜 [btn:Pulse Vac] 鎸夐敭杩涜鐪熺┖鎶芥皵銆?",
              "text_id": "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step3.text"
            },
            {
              "id": "step4",
              "text": "鏉惧紑鎸夐敭鍒欐殏鍋滄娊姘斻€?",
              "text_id": "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step4.text"
            },
            {
              "id": "step5",
              "text": "杈惧埌鎵€闇€鐪熺┖鐘舵€佸悗锛岀偣鍑?[btn:Seal] 鎸夐敭杩涜瀵嗗皝銆?",
              "text_id": "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step5.text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "notice_box",
          "text": "鍦ㄦ墜鍔ㄧ湡绌鸿繃绋嬩腑锛岄暱鎸夋寜閿娊姘旓紝鏉惧紑鏆傚仠锛屾鏃朵細澶勪簬淇濆帇鐨勭姸鎬併€傝嫢 10 绉掑唴涓嶈繘琛屽啀娆℃搷浣滐紝鏈哄櫒灏嗚嚜鍔ㄩ噴鏀惧帇鍔涳紝骞堕€€鍑烘墜鍔ㄦ娊姘旀ā寮忋€?",
          "text_id": "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.6.text"
        }
      ],
